{
  "stem": "17720.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is the reason why you, you see all the time the greatest talent of Israel leaving Israel and arranging their life here, like Perlman-- Itzhak Perlman, Zukerman, and many others-- many others, more or less known people.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I succeed to win a scholarship-- full scholarship for the Accademia di Santa Cecilia in Italy, in Rome.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is where I went from Israel-- there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I become, in Rome, concertmaster of Rome Opera.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I stay there also for a number of years, until [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that it happened that they came to the United States for performances.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Rome Opera came here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I received here offer from Metropolitan Opera in New York.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What year is this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time-- this was the year of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] '68, '68, '69.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] From the general manager at the time, Rudolf Bing, to join Metropolitan Opera-- it's much better conditions, in every respect, in every respect.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, there, I was not able to-- never to really receive the citizen-- Italian citizenship in one normal way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here, was supposed-- a different situation altogether.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Besides that, the conditions-- economic conditions-- totally different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one other thing that I find out that I-- was fascinating at the time was that-- I find out that in New York, which is a much more international city, I felt much more at home than in once-- Italian city, in which the nationalistic element-- the national element is much more powerful, much stronger.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And here, I agreed again to move my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I came to United States.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] This new page open now with opening new possibilities my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still never lost my desire to concertize.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
